ore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2014年,  800名ISIS 攻打摩蘇爾<br />\n當時摩蘇爾有三萬 伊拉克守軍........結果三萬守軍被 800名ISIS打走<br />\n印象深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原本伊拉克軍隊 都唔夠ISIS打<br />\n後來 美國 忍唔住...出動戰機空襲ISIS, 炸左差唔多一年, 伊拉克軍隊先可以成功反攻<br />\n<br />\n仲有美國提供左大量坦克, 裝甲車, 裝備 比伊拉克軍隊"},{"pid":"ac17937f865681a7a0af6c1bd26ae6c240c5cf14","tid":85814,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T11:28:12.000Z","msg":"呢個地方有咩戰略價值要全力進攻？"},{"pid":"20947a2721e188c379cce14d5022c2c55d6ad345","tid":85814,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:35:20.000Z","msg":"IS攻左代爾祖爾好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本係圍城,但攻唔入,睇下今次點"},{"pid":"67c13f8efacac450c1178dd481079d0793a0beb4","tid":85814,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8679e44fc5cad0df09d6f96feda23366a034b5","tid":85814,"uid":63212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}